'''Shikinai Shrine List of Mikawa Province''' (三河国の式内社一覧) is a list of the shrines (so‑called {{ill|Shikinai Shrines|de|Shikinai-Schreine|ja|式内社|zh|式内社}}) recorded under Mikawa Province in volumes 9–10 of the {{ill|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|de|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|ja|延喜式神名帳|zh|延喜式神名帳}}. Shrines existing at time of compilation but not listed (so‑called {{ill|Shikige Shrines|de|Shikige-Schreine|ja|式外社|zh|式外社}}) are noted separately.
==Shikinai Shrines (式内社)== The Engishiki Jinmyōchō lists 26 seats (25 distinct shrines) of the minor rank.
{{List of Shikinaisha/Legend}}
{| class="wikitable" style="background:#ffffff; font-size:85%" ! style="background:#a0f0a0" colspan=4 | {{ill|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|de|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|ja|延喜式神名帳|zh|延喜式神名帳}} ! style="background:#a0f0a0" colspan=3 | Designated Shrine ! style="background:#a0f0a0" rowspan=2 | Compilation |- style="white-space:nowrap;" ! style="background:#a0f0a0; padding:0.5em;" | Shrine Name ! style="background:#a0f0a0; padding:0.5em;" | Reading ! style="background:#a0f0a0; padding:0.5em;" | Rank ! style="background:#a0f0a0; padding:0.5em;" | Note ! style="background:#a0f0a0; padding:0.5em;" | Shrine Name ! style="background:#a0f0a0; padding:0.5em;" | Location ! style="background:#a0f0a0; padding:0.5em;" | Remarks |- |colspan=8 style="background-color:#ccffcc;"|'''{{ill|Kamo District|de|Kamo District|ja|賀茂郡|zh|賀茂郡}}''' 7 seats (Standard Minor) |- |'''Nomi Shrine'''||nomino||Shikinai Shōsha||||{{ill|Nomi Shrine|de|Nomi-Schrein|ja|野見神社|zh|野见神社}}||Aichi Prefecture, Toyota City, Nomiyama‑chō|||| |- |'''Nogi Shrine'''||nogi||Shikinai Shōsha||||{{ill|Nogi Shrine|de|Nogi-Schrein|ja|野神社|zh|野神社}}||Aichi Prefecture, Toyota City, Noguchi‑mizu‑betsu Himen|||| |- |'''Hōshu Shrine'''||hōshu||Shikinai Shōsha||||{{ill|Hōshu Shrine|de|Hōshu-Schrein|ja|兵主神社|zh|兵主神社}}||Aichi Prefecture, Toyota City, Arai‑machi Matsushima|||| |- |'''Iho Shrine'''||ihono||Shikinai Shōsha||||{{ill|Iho Shrine|de|Iho-Schrein|ja|射穂神社|zh|射穂神社}}||Aichi Prefecture, Toyota City, Homi‑chō Kitayama|||| |- |'''Sanage Shrine'''||sanage||Shikinai Shōsha||||{{ill|Sanage Shrine|de|Sanage-Schrein|ja|猿投神社|zh|猿投神社}}||Aichi Prefecture, Toyota City, Sanage‑chō||Mikawa Province Sannomiya{{Sfn|中世諸国一宮制|2000|p=127}}||[http://21coe.kokugakuin.ac.jp/db/jinja/100401.html] |- |'''Hirosawa Shrine'''||hirosawano||Shikinai Shōsha||||{{ill|Hirosawa Tianjin Shrine|de|Hirosawa-Tianjin-Schrein|ja|広沢天神社|zh|广泽天神社}}||Aichi Prefecture, Toyota City, Sanage‑chō Oguro‑mi|||| |- |'''Haibaho Shrine'''||haibaho||Shikinai Shōsha||||{{ill|Haibaho Shrine|de|Haibaho-Sc