'''Shikinai Shrine List of Mikawa Province''' (三河国の式内社一覧) is a list of the shrines (so‑called {{ill|Shikinai Shrines|de|Shikinai-Schreine|ja|式内社|zh|式内社}}) recorded under Mikawa Province in volumes 9–10 of the {{ill|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|de|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|ja|延喜式神名帳|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyocho|zh|延喜式神名帳}}. Shrines existing at time of compilation but not listed (so‑called {{ill|Shikige Shrines|de|Shikige-Schreine|ja|式外社|zh|式外社}}) are noted separately.
==Shikinai Shrines (式内社)== The Engishiki Jinmyōchō lists 26 seats (25 distinct shrines) of the minor Rank.
