[[sn:List of Shikinaisha in Mikawa Province]] [[ja:三河国の式内社一覧]] [[de:Liste der Shikinaisha in Mikawa Province]]

[[Category: Lists of Shikinaisha by location top]][[Category: Lists of Shikinaisha by location top]]This is a '''List of Shikinaisha in Mikawa Province'''. Or the list of shrines in [[Mikawa Province]] which is present in the {{ill|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyocho|ja|延喜式神名帳|12=draft}}. On this page we will also cover the {{ill|Shikigeisha|ja|式外社|1=Shikigeisha|12=draft}} of [[Mikawa Province]] which are shrines that are known to have existed at that time due to other historical records, such as the [[Rikkokushi]], but for some reason were excluded from the {{ill|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyocho|ja|延喜式神名帳|12=draft}}. We will cover them in a separate list to avoid confusion.
<!--{{afc comment|1=Used substitution to get all the templates into here relatively easily. On enwiki if you want the templates extract them out of this page to make templates, The jawiki system is too hard—[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 05:35, 31 March 2025 (UTC)}} {{afc comment|1=Page target for move is at List of Shikinaisha in Mikawa Province—[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 09:49, 26 March 2025 (UTC)}} {{afc comment|1=Switching over to deprecating the templates. So things might be a bit unexpected.—[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 05:01, 18 March 2025 (UTC)}}
'''Shikinai Shrine List of Mikawa Province''' (三河国の式内社一覧) is a list of the shrines (so‑called {{ill|Shikinai Shrines|de|Shikinai-Schreine|ja|式内社|zh|式内社|12=draft}}) recorded under Mikawa Province in volumes 9–10 of the {{ill|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|de|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|ja|延喜式神名帳|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyocho|zh|延喜式神名帳|12=draft}}. Shrines existing at time of compilation but not listed (so‑called {{ill|Shikige Shrines|de|Shikige-Schreine|ja|式外社|zh|式外社|12=draft}}) are noted separately.
--> == Shikinai Shrines (式内社) == The Engishiki Jinmyōchō lists 26 seats (25 distinct shrines) of the minor Rank.
